rows.name: ...Huh? You want to know why I'm waiting in line?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016801_MSG0002
rows.name: You mean you don't even know who she is?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016801_MSG0003
rows.name:

bloomed on this miserable world![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016801_MSG0004

I've been waiting in line all morning just for a chance
to speak with her![ST:wait ]
